{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7121e3b74a","title":"对人民日报理论工作的批评","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8e67c0a789","index":0,"year":1964,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"7121e3b74a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d9cbbf96fe","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：说“尽可能的长寿”，这好。只可以尽可能活得长一点，不可能不死。中国历史上","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"94a9597a92","type":"paragraph","text":"还没那回事。你们回去后，请代我问候你们总统，说我配他身体健康，工作顺利，克服困难，向","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"d62c76ea84","type":"paragraph","text":"前发展。纳比：主席先生，非常威谢您接见了我们。您栖性了您的时间，本来您还有极其重要的工","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"6b6a8492df","type":"paragraph","text":"作。我想向您表达阿尔及利亚人民的敬意。是您领导了中国伟大的革命事业。我想表示的是，阿尔及利亚人民对中国有发自内心的友好感情，他们有共同的敌人，就是殖民主义。他们的斗争所处的条件，也几乎是一样的。我们知道你们是夺取了敌人的武器战胜了敌人的。阿尔及利亚人民也是从法国军队手里夺取了武器打珍法国军队的。","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"d562056fe8","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要向中国人民表示惠心的敬意。主席：要向你们国家的人民表示敬意，向你们国家的领导人表示敬意。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"dabac857fd","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的本·具拉总统的全名怎么写？","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"f3c4891783","type":"paragraph","text":"（翻译用纸条写好，主席阅毕收存。纳比：谢谢您，再一次向您表示惠心的敬意。威谢您的热情接待。主席：谢谢。再见。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"4ed9e6a7e2","type":"paragraph","text":"（主席同全体外宾合影留念）对人民日报理输工作的批部","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"6bba970c04","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年四月）","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"5c553f4647","type":"paragraph","text":"《人民日报》的理论工作是应付我的，谁管理论版？（答：陈凌）让王若水管好了，他的文章多吗？","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"8dccf1e4dd","type":"paragraph","text":"关于胡藏芸案件的指示和批示","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"d5926f7ba4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年四月）","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"0a9570682e","type":"paragraph","text":"你看，确有此事吧！有些人只爱物，不爱人，只重生产，不重改造。把犯人当成劳役，只有压服不行。其实抓紧思想政治工作，以思想工作第一，作好这一面，不仅不会姑碍生产，相反还会促进生产。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"9554104be3","type":"paragraph","text":"（1964年4月，同汪东兴同志的谈蓄）人是可以改造的，就是政策和方法要正确才行。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"b60140871e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1964年4月20日，对公安部党组关于调查处理胡藏芸案件的情况报告的批示）","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"},{"id":"76f7c4fe2c","type":"paragraph","text":"109。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a"}],"page":{"id":"ce03722cb0","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"7121e3b74a","start":122,"end":122}}}},"__N_SSG":true}